list.abstract: 《Priority》是爱内里菜（あいうち りな）演唱的日语流行歌曲，RINA AIUCHI作词，KENTARO ISHII作曲，发行于2010年9月15日，收录于专辑《LAST SCENE》中。

yingyinNormal.en: System, locate Dr. Ford for me. Send him a message, highest priority.
yingyinNormal.zh: 系统，帮我定位福特博士，向他发送消息，使用最高优先权。

yingyinNormal.en: Priority call from Secretary Ross. There's been a breach at the Raft Prison. Yeah, put him through.
yingyinNormal.zh: 国务卿罗斯的优先来电，孤岛监狱遭人劫狱。嗯，接过来。

yingyinNormal.en: Honey, I think Eric's employing a broad-based concept of value of friendship taking priority...
yingyinNormal.zh: 亲爱的，我觉得艾瑞克是在阐述友谊广泛意义上的价值，要优先……

yingyinNormal.en: We're talking about a being whose very existence challenges our own sense of priority in the universe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们现在在讨论的这个人，他的存在挑战了我们自身对事物优先级别的认知。

yingyinNormal.en: And as our civilian and military personnel serve in the region, their safety and health will remain a top priority.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有我们在这一地区的平民和军事人员，他们的安全和健康将仍然是最优先的事情。

yingyinNormal.en: Our priority must be to stop the gate from opening. Fail there, and it's just a matter of time before they beat us with sheer numbers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们必须优先阻止传送门打开，如果那里失败，在他们以绝对数量击败我们之前只是一个时间问题了。

yingyinNormal.en: You must catch these men, Commander Bromley. Again, it's our top priority.
yingyinNormal.zh: 布罗姆尼长官，您一定要抓到凶手。放心，这是我们工作的重中之重。

yingyinNormal.en: As Commander in Chief, my highest priority is the security of the American people.
yingyinNormal.zh: 作为最高统帅，我最首要的任务就是保证美国人民的安宁。

yingyinNormal.en: And City Hall is right up my tail to find them. This is priority number one. Assignments.
yingyinNormal.zh: 市政厅天天追在我屁股后面，这是头等大事，任务分配。

yingyinNormal.en: Starting tomorrow, I am turning over a new leaf. Time with you is my number one priority.
yingyinNormal.zh: 明天起我会重新做人，和你在一起才是头等大事。

yingyinNormal.en: But our top priority is a first concession. Proof of life. So you'll promise nothing. Okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但最重要的任务是证明人质还活着。所以你什么都不承诺。好的。

yingyinNormal.en: He just lost eight soldiers. Talking to their families is his priority as it would be mine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他刚失去八名士兵，他现在首先要和他们的家人谈话，换做是我也会这样做。

yingyinNormal.en: Prime Minister, your life is in danger. I think our first priority is to move you to a secure location.
yingyinNormal.zh: 首相大人，您正处于危险当中，我认为我们的首要任务是把您转移至安全的地方。

yingyinNormal.en: Look. Cost-cutting is clearly a priority for you, look at the size of your kitchen, teeny tiny. Must be a bit annoying when you're such a keen cook.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瞧。你非常在意省钱，看看你的厨房，太小了。你这么喜欢烹饪，肯定很苦恼。

yingyinNormal.en: I assure you, this investigation is our top priority, Mr. Quan. And we're doing all we can and pursuing every possible lead to find those who killed your daughter.
yingyinNormal.zh: 关先生，我向您保证这案件是我们现在的首要任务。我们正竭尽所能，追查每一条线索力求找到杀害您女儿的凶手。

yingyinNormal.en: Last question. In a post-apocalyptic world, which task would you assign the highest priority? Locating a sustainable food source, reestablishing a functioning government, procreating, or preserving the knowledge of mankind?
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后一个问题，身处一个后启示录的世界中，你会最先考虑完成以下哪项工作：找出可持续利用的食物来源，重建一个功能政府，生育，还是传承人类文化？
